- `NO_VIDEO_TRACK`: Source has no video track for video rendition
- `URL_MISMATCH`: Request URL doesn't match signed URL token

**Error Context Included**:

- Error ID (8-char hex)
- Timestamp
- Request method, URL, query params
- User agent, IP address
- Additional context (sourceUrl, rendition, segmentId, etc.)

